    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Spineremaeus smithi gen. et sp. nov., paratype female; a) right leg I, axial; b) left leg II, anti-axial; c) left leg III anti-axial; d) left leg IV, anti-axial. Pori are on axial surfaces." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/206956/files/figure.png" ;
